Interface CompileToJarStepFactory

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RuleKeyAppendable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseCompileToJarStepFactory, JavacToJarStepFactory, KotlincToJarStepFactory, ScalacToJarStepFactory

    public interface CompileToJarStepFactory
extends RuleKeyAppendable
    Creates the necessary steps to compile the source files, apply post process classes commands, and pack the output .class files into a Jar.
